Cell[TextData[{
 "It is sometimes useful to build",
 StyleBox[" your own package",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ", in particular when there are functions/operations that you use very often \
and keep redefining in new notebooks.\nLet\[CloseCurlyQuote]s use a simple \
example of a package to illustrate how it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s done. "
}], "Text",
